%% ModelMesh Serving - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant REST as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(OVMS/Triton)
    participant Puller as Storage Puller<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Model Inference (via OAuth)
    Client->>OAuth: HTTPS :8443<br/>OpenShift OAuth Token
    OAuth->>OAuth: SAR validation<br/>(services/get on namespace)
    OAuth->>REST: HTTP :8008<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    REST->>MM: gRPC :8033<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    MM->>Runtime: gRPC (pod-internal)<br/>No encryption
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction Result
    MM-->>REST: gRPC Response
    REST-->>OAuth: HTTP Response
    OAuth-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Direct gRPC Inference
    Client->>MM: gRPC :8033<br/>TLS (optional) / mTLS (optional)
    MM->>Runtime: gRPC (pod-internal)
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction Result
    MM-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Model Registration
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event<br/>Predictor/InferenceService CR
    Controller->>MM: gRPC :8033<br/>Register vmodel
    MM->>etcd: gRPC :2379<br/>TLS (optional)<br/>Username/Password auth
    etcd-->>MM: Confirmation
    MM-->>Controller: Registration OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: HTTPS :6443<br/>Update CR status<br/>ServiceAccount token

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Model Loading
    MM->>Puller: gRPC :8086<br/>(pod-internal)
    Puller->>S3: HTTPS :443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / Access Keys
    S3-->>Puller: Model Artifacts
    Puller->>Runtime: gRPC (pod-internal)<br/>Load model
    Runtime-->>MM: Model Ready

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 5: etcd Event Streaming
    Controller->>etcd: gRPC Watch :2379<br/>TLS (optional)<br/>Username/Password
    etcd-->>Controller: Model/vmodel state changes
    Controller->>K8sAPI: HTTPS :6443<br/>Update CR status
